r BIT students\n            \n          \n        \n\n        \n        \n          EDUCATION\n          \n            \n              \n              Bachelor's in Information Technology\n              Patan Multiple Campus, TU • 2021 – 2025\n            \n            \n              \n              Physical Science (Higher Secondary)\n              Deep Boarding High School, NEB • 2018 – 2020\n            \n          \n        \n\n        \n        \n          SKILLS & TOOLS\n          \n            TypeScript\n            React\n            Next.js\n            FastAPI\n            Python\n            Tailwind\n            PostgreSQL\n            Docker\n            MongoDB\n            Git\n          \n        \n\n        \n        \n          \n            Let's work together\n            aghimire074@gmail.com\n          \n          \n            GitHub ↗\n            Email ↗\n          \n        \n\n      \n    \n    \n      Minimal + Timeline — Full Page Layout\n      Clean minimal aesthetic throughout. Timeline used for Experience and Education. Bordered cards for Projects. Badge pills for Skills. Sticky navbar with dark/light toggle. Click to approve this design.","choice":"approved","id":null,"timestamp":1774370369722}
